。報道指皇馬軍醫為泰拔高圖爾斯進行連串檢查後，證實佢患上嚴重焦慮症。<br />\n<br />\n消息傳出後，西班牙各大媒體都大事報道，泰拔高圖爾斯已經連續2日未有隨大軍操練，相信會無限期休戰，直到焦慮症問題完全解決，周六(6號)晚主場對CF格蘭納達嘅聯賽，上陣機會渺茫。<br />\n<br />\n致病原因係乜暫時未知，不過西班牙著名記者Zach Lowy透露，球迷嘅猛烈批評，以及奧比歷同達史特根今季嘅出色表現，都令泰拔高圖爾斯感受到極大壓力。西班牙《阿斯報》更報道，皇馬教練施丹準備同佢割席，明年1月打算收購AC米蘭門將基安盧基當拿隆馬頂替。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/YPBZC74.png\" /></blockquote><br />\n慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c554bc6811fb8be9709992079a28eeefa0205bd","tid":1617950,"uid":16343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:35:05.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 25仔"},{"pid":"5f923d894f666b15d8a273c07806a7241fff5ee0","tid":1617950,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:38:04.000Z","msg":"拿華斯咁好用唔要 要件垃圾"},{"pid":"5819458edfe7f818e4b3b15cd77544eb1ce9c9a2","tid":1617950,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m1hi2Yo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm1hi2Yo.jpg&h=0a8dda74&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfdb49b5921de573b1babe66e1ef7256c2cb32af","tid":1617950,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d03882a375a3a4d0e9864154e1fa837d3139c303","tid":1617950,"uid":38189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7fc2a133b14b947e183baa0d7b2df960ad77ea66","tid":1617950,"uid":48379,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T03:12:35.000Z","msg":"皇馬同共產黨一樣  佩雷斯一日仲要管  皇馬唔會翻到身"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T03:34:03.000Z","msg":"三連冠個主席係邊個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:50:53.000Z","msg":"err......er......er......"},{"pid":"b8f2948b79e54b89ffa881de1888bdb9ac34b023","tid":161